e":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be4485751ffaacae8077bf6ded47cf962faeb73b","tid":1699584,"uid":2429,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:06:48.000Z","msg":"人地停課都屌，肯罷工未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AxeN9ge.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAxeN9ge.jpg&h=69dfcf07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/93d3sB8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F93d3sB8.jpg&h=cb63a975&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n手足只係condom，議席最重要。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:30:15.000Z","msg":"常見問題<br />\n1. 幾時罷工呀？<br />\n其實罷工有好多前期準備工作，唔係定個日子就可以罷。一來要處理錢嘅問題，需要有罷工基金support，而罷工基金往往係由工會處理返自己個行業。二來要處理邊際成本嘅問題，例如成間公司得一個人罷，甚至有藍絲篤灰，老闆要炒話咁易，但如果成間公司有一半人罷工就好唔同。<br />\n<br />\n2. 咁點樣處理上述講嘅問題？<br />\n罷工好多時會有前期嘅行業行動，例如搵一日係網上call支持罷工嘅人集體dress code或者一齊戴朵花，又或者85三罷前嘅行業集會，咁你就可以由網絡延伸到real contact，知道實質你所處嘅職場有幾多係自己人，繼而造成組織，由自己working place去到隔離公司，甚至成個地區或行業。另一個方法就係工會，以成為會員嘅方式組成real contact，再用工會名義發起罷工。<br />\n<br />\n3. 我可以做啲咩？<br />\n幫手reach你自己行業嘅人，或者參與成立你所屬行業嘅工會。仲有share呢個群組出去，等呢度可以凝聚到更多有意有心罷工嘅人。<br />\n成立工會程序可參照 <a href=\"https://t.me/hkonstrike/63\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkonstrike%2F63&d=6wykgBqlsxypO2QI0oCEUiWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=22fe58a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkonstrike/63</a>"},{"pid":"b072a61acb5cd81b2fb6603ee2e3fbf25795e37c","tid":1699584,"uid":263563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a3589cbaf32b3be4ff6f5b349bbd006b0c26cfee","tid":1699584,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be4485751ffaacae8077bf6ded47cf962faeb73b","tid":1699584,"uid":2429,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:06:48.000Z","msg":"人地停課都屌，肯罷工未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://